comment: LHH shows that Afflalo (NYK) cleanly strips the ball from Cousins (SAC) and that the ball touches Cousins' body prior to going OOB.
Calderon (NYK) sets the screen on Cousins (SAC) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LATR and RATR shows that Cousins (SAC) sets the screen on Vujacic (NYK) and gives him room to avoid the contact. After the screen, the two players briefly engage and separate.
LHH shows that Porzingis (NYK) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Cousins' (SAC) move to the basket and shot attempt. Cousins is the last player to touch the ball prior to it going OOB.
Afflalo (NYK) makes contact with Casspi's (SAC) arm that affects his layup attempt.
Rondo (SAC) makes contact with Porzingis' (NYK) arm and body that affects his putback shot attempt.
Galloway (NYK) commits a take foul on Collison (SAC).
Afflalo (NYK) cleanly strips the ball from Collison (SAC) but never gains possession in the front court which allows him to go into the backcourt to gain possession of the ball.
Rondo (SAC) grabs Anthony's (NYK) arm prior to the start of his upward shooting motion and affects his RSBQ.
